{"tid":829760,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"甩拖無人養　Jumbo：女人要有工作先可以鞏固愛情","createTime":"2018-09-20T16:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T20:52:31.000Z","uid":157545,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cffb12d4f5643e38ab6b5f455af7f2e3f5890847","tid":829760,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1886778/org/5d2aafa3b7dacf2fb8b375cf2a45c450.jpg/YlQRXuinq7hayczUdH3myqVp80COAfPRxD6-ZcQ-vmU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1886778%2Forg%2F5d2aafa3b7dacf2fb8b375cf2a45c450.jpg%2FYlQRXuinq7hayczUdH3myqVp80COAfPRxD6-ZcQ-vmU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2e63da61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n27歲女神曾淑雅（Jumbo）選美入行以來，一雙長腿加上甜美的酒窩俘虜不少宅男。今年年初， Jumbo被影到與圈外才俊男友蜜遊台灣，但她接受《香港01》訪問時就自爆已經同男友分手。Jumbo表示：「依家單身，分咗手了。（幾時嘅事？）啱啱。（咩原因？）見光死啩，其實我好多朋友都唔想出鏡，所以我IG都好少Post朋友嘅樣。（涉唔涉及第三者？）無呀，我哋和平分手，依家仲係朋友！（準備好迎接新戀情未呀？）仲傷心緊&hellip;因為我以前細個比較鍾意黐住另一半。但依家覺得女人一定要有工作，先可以鞏固自己的愛情，所以我都會以工作為先。」<br />\n<br />\nJumbo19歲時參加中國小姐香港區成為三料冠軍入行，雖然參與過不少電影演出，包括《小姐誘心》、《PG戀愛指引》以及《空手道》等，但表現都未算突出，反而索爆身材就引起不少討論。問到入行8年仍未有代表作會否感到可惜，她稱：「唔會，每個人的經歷嚟嘅，其實有得拍戲已經好開心，可以喺銀幕見到自己都好難得。（但呢排好少見到你演出？）其實我都有返內地拍網劇，好似同梁烈唯拍嘅《失業皇帝2017》，旱排都拍咗一部未上叫《來自前度的炸彈》，兩套都係女主角。」<br />\n<br />\nJumbo簽約向展邦和向展威模特兒公司多年，下年就正式約滿八年，問到會否續約，Jumbo就表示：「其實我都有同公司同事表達過想轉型做健身教練，因為我都已經考咗教練牌。（所以唔會續約？）啲嘢又唔可以講到咁實，想嚟緊向健身呢個方向發展，希望兩邊都兼顧到，因為香港藝人專做一邊比較難，而且我都鍾意演戲，可能到時有打女的角色，我健開身可以即刻做到。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1886780/org/9f9e6d2ebc8258d9adebc5fd80c7e0d1.jpg/wKyZMQhb63vNM_75BUfH_t2WeZ3rDdFv-2_FmftvxZk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1886780%2Forg%2F9f9e6d2ebc8258d9adebc5fd80c7e0d1.jpg%2FwKyZMQhb63vNM_75BUfH_t2WeZ3rDdFv-2_FmftvxZk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8b36ecf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9c89614eb46f9fc993760e9a22879b5651a60af","tid":829760,"uid":28574,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:07:15.000Z","msg":"正過fyy好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1240d87f203164c9dc7541a627220f95073e32","tid":829760,"uid":17268,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"佢身形做教練無乜說服性喎"},{"pid":"8e36514efddc78b0d3f59e7b4e837e7ff26c878a","tid":829760,"uid":110486,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4d1240d87f203164c9dc7541a627220f95073e32","tid":829760,"uid":17268,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"佢身形做教練無乜說服性喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"老實講我就唔介意嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cf8d77a95acbd8e4055dab9ee23dc444cbd09b","tid":829760,"uid":169468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"呢條女係正<br />\n<br />\n但冇乜主角相"},{"pid":"c596ace1252281baca53a43e4c36af7e40e51684","tid":829760,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a764b0cb63d1a59d92745d1a8da04ad6e1c435","tid":829760,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:19:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會係被人包去台灣？"},{"pid":"795062e08e8a444753ebcfa49b595205c4401c80","tid":829760,"uid":135986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d1240d87f203164c9dc7541a627220f95073e32","tid":829760,"uid":17268,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"佢身形做教練無乜說服性喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"大把女人想搵佢操<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔谷唔代表佢無肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e18af06995fc293c027abcdfe9